import React, {useState} from 'react'
import { Button } from './Button'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import './Navbar.css'
import Dropdown from './Dropdown'

function Navbar(){
    return(
        <>
        <nav className='navbar'>
            <link to='/' className='navbar-logo'>
                EPIC
            </link>
        </nav>
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar;
